This skill ports concepts (baseline+diff loop, selector filters, significance
thresholding, notify-on-change) from changedetection.io by dgtlmoon, which is
licensed Apache-2.0: https://github.com/dgtlmoon/changedetection.io

The stdlib runner in scripts/watch.py is an original, independent reimplementation
of those concepts (no upstream code copied) and is provided under the same terms.

